OL,5,EI'VE SENIOR ON THE TELLY!              
OL,7,BLots of people would love to be a      
OL,8,ETV presenter,Bbut for unemployed Andy  
OL,9,BSenior it couldn't have been easier!   
OL,10,B                                       
OL,11,BThe 25-year-oldBimpressed the producers
OL,12,Bof Channel 4'sEMoviewatchBso much when 
OL,13,Bhe appeared on the show as a reviewer, 
OL,14,Bthey asked him to become theirEroving  
OL,15,Ereporter!                              
OL,17,BNow, as Club discovered, quick-witted  
OL,18,BYorkshireman Andy is hobnobbing with   
OL,19,Bthe likes ofEBrad Pitt!                
