OL,4,G`````````````````````````````W==,,=5G``
OL,5,EI'VE SENIOR ON THE TELLY!              
OL,7,BOpinionated reviewerEAndy SeniorBwasn't
OL,8,Bafraid to slag off a film when he      
OL,9,Bappeared on Moviewatch as a panellist. 
OL,11,B"I was a harsh-talking, sardonic       
OL,12,BYorkshireman!" he confesses. "I said   
OL,13,EKeanu ReevesBwas wooden inEChain       
OL,14,EReaction!BI hatedEThe English Patient  
OL,15,Bbecause I was sick of seeing Dorset    
OL,16,Btoffs poncing about in the desert."    
OL,18,B"I even had a row aboutERomeo And      
OL,19,EJulietBwith one of the other guests!"  
