OL,4,G`````````````````````````````W==,,=5G``
OL,5,EI'VE SENIOR ON THE TELLY!              
OL,7,BUnemployed film buffEAndy SeniorBhad no
OL,8,Bexperience of interviewing when        
OL,9,BMoviewatch bosses asked him to be their
OL,10,ErovingEreporter.                       
OL,12,B"Now I do set reports and interview    
OL,13,Bdirectors and stars," he says. "Last   
OL,14,Bweek I flew to Toronto to meetEBrad    
OL,15,EPitt."B(lucky devil!)                  
OL,17,B"His shirt wasEopen to the navel!BI was
OL,18,Bnot in awe of meeting him. If you are, 
OL,19,Byou can't do the interview properly."  
