OL,4,G`````````````````````````````W==,,=5G``
OL,5,EI'VE SENIOR ON THE TELLY!              
OL,7,BMoviewatch's new reporter Andy Senior  
OL,8,Bdid a degree in media studies and was  
OL,9,Ehoping to become a comedianBwith a pal 
OL,10,Bof his when he got his lucky break.    
OL,12,B"We made spoof films. One was a rip-off
OL,13,Bof Broken Arrow, about two allotment   
OL,14,Bgardeners. It was calledEBroken Marrow!
OL,16,B"I've always been a movie buff. I go to
OL,17,Bthe cinema every week. My favourite    
OL,18,Bactress isESharon Stone.BI just hope   
OL,19,Bshe finds Yorkshiremen attractive!"    
