OL,4,G`````````````````````````````W==,,=5G``
OL,5,EI'VE SENIOR ON THE TELLY!              
OL,7,BMoviewatch's newcomerEAndy SeniorBsays 
OL,8,BBrits should adopt a moreEAmerican     
OL,9,Bapproach when they go to the cinema.   
OL,11,B"I like it when people join in with the
OL,12,Baction,Ewhooping and yellingBif        
OL,13,Bsomething big happens," he tells Club. 
OL,15,B"The worst film I've seen recently was 
OL,16,EMars Attacks!BIt was trying too hard to
OL,17,Bbe funny. IBlove B-moviesBthough. My   
OL,18,Bfavourite film isEDawn Of The Mummy.BIt
OL,19,Bis a horror that's so bad it's good!"  
